panels.content:
<center><input onchange="changeTimeSelected(event)" id="daySelector" type="date"/></center>

<script>


const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
var currentFrom = urlParams.get("var-timeFrom");
var currentTo = urlParams.get("var-timeTo");

var datePickTo;
var datePickFrom;
if (currentFrom && currentTo){
  datePickFrom = new Date(parseFloat(currentFrom));
  datePickTo = new Date(parseFloat(currentTo));
}
else{
  datePickTo = new Date();
  datePickTo.setHours(0,0,0,0);
  datePickFrom = new Date(datePickTo.getTime() - 150800000);
  var newUrl = updateGrafanaVariableAndGetUrl("timeFrom", datePickFrom.getTime());
  newUrl = updateGrafanaVariableAndGetUrl("timeTo", datePickTo.getTime(), newUrl);
  setUrl(newUrl);
}
document.getElementById('daySelector').valueAsDate = datePickFrom;



function updateGrafanaVariableAndGetUrl(variable, value, href){
  
    var hash       = {};
    var parser     = document.createElement('a');
    var param = "var-" + variable;

    parser.href    = href ? href : location.href;

    var parameters = parser.search.split(/\?|&/);

    for(var i=0; i < parameters.length; i++) {
        if(!parameters[i])
            continue;

        var ary      = parameters[i].split('=');
        hash[ary[0]] = ary[1];
    }

    hash[param] = value;

    var list = [];  
    Object.keys(hash).forEach(function (key) {
        list.push(key + '=' + hash[key]);
    });

    parser.search = '?' + list.join('&');
    return parser.href;
}

function setUrl(url){
  location.href = url;
}


function changeTimeSelected(event){
  var dateSelected = new Date(event.target.value);
  var timeFrom = dateSelected.getTime();
  var timeTo = timeFrom + 86400000;
  console.log(timeFrom + " - " + timeTo);
  var newUrl = updateGrafanaVariableAndGetUrl("timeFrom", timeFrom);
  newUrl = updateGrafanaVariableAndGetUrl("timeTo", timeTo, newUrl);
  setUrl(newUrl);
}

</script>

SELECT count(cumpliendo) / (count(nocumpliendo)+count(cumpliendo)) AS Ratio1
FROM (
SELECT guaranteeValue as cumpliendo FROM metrics.autogen.metrics_values WHERE guaranteeResult = true AND "id" = 'DISPONIBILIDAD_ALTA_ACTIVIDAD' AND time >= [[timeFrom]]ms AND time <= [[timeTo]]ms AND "scope_servicio" =~ /^$Servicio$/)
,
(
SELECT guaranteeValue as nocumpliendo FROM metrics.autogen.metrics_values WHERE guaranteeResult = false AND "id" = 'DISPONIBILIDAD_ALTA_ACTIVIDAD' AND time >= [[timeFrom]]ms AND time <= [[timeTo]]ms AND "scope_servicio" =~ /^$Servicio$/
)
